zai---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Budget Ergonomic Office Chair 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of ergonomic chairs under $150. Support your back during 8-hour workdays.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Budget Ergonomic Office Chair</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · Under $150</div>

      <p>A good ergonomic chair is essential for anyone who spends long hours at a desk. After testing multiple budget options, one stands out for providing premium features at an affordable price point — supporting your back without breaking the bank.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 Hbada Ergonomic Office Chair</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>S-shaped backrest mimics spine curve</strong> — natural posture support</li>
          <li><strong>Adjustable lumbar support and headrest</strong> — customizable comfort</li>
          <li><strong>3D armrests move up/down and swivel</strong> — perfect arm positioning</li>
          <li><strong>Breathable mesh back, padded seat cushion</strong> — cool and comfortable</li>
          <li><strong>155-degree recline with footrest extension</strong> — relaxation mode</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=ergonomic+office+chair&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it wins at this price</h3>
      <p>Most budget chairs compromise on adjustability or lumbar support. The Hbada offers 3D armrests, adjustable headrest, and a recline function that's rare under $150. The S-shaped backrest follows your spine's natural curve, reducing back pain during long work sessions.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Remote workers, students, and anyone who wants proper ergonomic support without spending $500+ on premium chairs. It's perfect for 8-hour workdays and provides excellent value for the price.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>